      "text": "Georgetown, Ohio is the proud hometown of President Ulysses S. Grant, an influential military leader and stalwart protector of civil rights.\n\nI’m proud to see the House pass my bill, H.R. 7809, designating the Georgetown post office as the “Ulysses S. Grant Post Office Building!” https://t.co/v714Qu6e0B",
