      "text": "Spot on.\n\nThe health of rural Ohioans hinges on their ability to access critical health care from rural providers. In an emergency, there’s not always time to drive to a major city for care. \n\nThat’s why I introduced the Defend Rural Health Act — to protect funds for rural",
